      "content": "it's honestly terrifying to think about. if they're actually doing this in real-time, like actively trying to influence my mood to see how i react... then i'm basically just a lab rat in my own house. what kind of measures could someone even take to stop this? if the hardware itself is the problem, how do i even know if i'm safe anymore?",
